Title: The Mayze
Plot: It's a new term at St Hearts and with Zoe still away, spy handler Frank tasks the elite spies with the mission of tracking down one of Zoe's remaining duplicants, Keri, who is the new intended host of the Mastermind's consciousness! It's becomes a race against time to reach Keri first and save her from the clutches of KORP.
ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification.  Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.
